    title: "How ML Models Predict Property Prices with 94% Accuracy",
    excerpt: "Deep dive into Automated Valuation Models (AVMs): the ML techniques behind Rightmove, Zoopla, and how to build a custom AVM for your property business.",
    author: "Oleksiy Kovalenko",
    category: "AI та Автоматизація",
    tags: ["ML", "Property Valuation", "AVM", "Real Estate", "Predictive Modelling"],
    date: "2026-05-02",
