      "## UK enterprise LLM у 2026\n\nDeloitte UK 2026: 67% FTSE 350 мають хоча б один LLM в production. Основні use cases: RAG knowledge retrieval, customer support automation, document summarisation, code assistance.",
      "## Вибір моделі: GPT-4o vs Claude 3.5 vs Llama 3.3\n\nGPT-4o → Azure OpenAI UK South (UK data residency). Claude 3.5 Sonnet → AWS Bedrock eu-west-2. Llama 3.3 70B → on-premises (NHS sensitive data, classified contracts, trading algorithms).",
